FUTURES_BILL_FUND_TYPE_TIPS:
It is the mechanics used to tether to spot price, applied every %s hours. Funding payment is based on the position value a user holds at the funding timestamp. If funding rate is positive, longs pay shorts; if negative, shorts pay longs. 
Funding = Position Value x Funding Rate
